Let t2mc_base be the base directory of tm2c installation.

1. Create the following directories:
   	  tm2c_base/external
   	  tm2c_base/external/include
     	  tm2c_base/external/lib

2. Install the libconfig library:
   	   ./configure --disable-cxx --prefix PATH_TO/tm2c_base/external
	   make install

3. For TM2C with shrimp (Nikola's MP lib):
       	    git clone http://lpdserver.epfl.ch/~knezevic/shrimp.git
	    mkdir shrimp/external
	    install khash.h <http://attractivechaos.awardspace.com/khash.h> into shrimp/external/include
	    install libatomic_ops using ./configure --prefix=LOCATION_OF_SHRIMP/EXTERNAL
	    build shrimp:
	    	  make clean 
		  make install PREFIX=LOCATION_OF_DTM/EXTERNAL

then you can go to tm2c_base and do: 
     	     make clean all

4. For TM2C with ssmp (my MP lib):
       	    git clone ssh://lpdserver.epfl.ch/~trigonak/devel/ssmp.git
	    make
	    copy ssmp.h into tm2c_base/external/include
	    copy libssmp.a into tm2c_base/external/lib
	    
then you can go to tm2c_base and do: 
     	     make clean all